Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:33.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}Ashes to ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:38.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}Soul to soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:50.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}I will say  Never again
